description:
Responsibilities:
Provide Dietetic services to service users of the DHC Express Scheme,  including direct assessment, treatment, program planning & implementation, be responsible for related documentation, communication & reporting;
Conduct primary health promotion, education talk & provide direct patient education & coaching;
As an active member of the multi-disciplinary team and primary healthcare resource hub to engage related service stakeholder and discipline for primary health & chronic disease management;
Provide professional inputs in service planning and development of the Scheme;
To supervise supporting staff, as required
Requirements:
Bachelor of Science in Dietetics plus internship and on list of Hong Kong Academy of Accredited Dietitian;
Possess 5 years or above post-qualification experience in patient care related practice in dietetic service, preferable both in clinical setting or in community setting;
Good interpersonal and problem-solving skills.
Possess good communication and presentation skills
Proactive, mature and independent; possess good computer literacy
Please send full resume with expected salary and reference no. quoted to Haven of Hope Christian Service, Staff Engagement Department, 7 Haven of Hope Road, Tseung Kwan O, New Territories or via email by clicking "Apply Now", or via Whatsapp no. 6507 8148 (with reference no. quoted at the caption) on or before 5 February 2022. Only short-listed candidates will be notified.


Enquiry: 2703 3227 (Phone); 6507 8148 (Whatsapp).


For details about our organization, please visit www.hohcs.org.hk.


Prospective employees are requested to undergo/submit Sexual Conviction Record Check for work relating to children or mentally incapacitated persons before employment. Data collected will be used for recruitment purpose only.


This advertisement should not be reproduced, in whole or in part, to other recruitment websites without our prior written permission.

工作內容:


接待客人及解問客人簡單查詢;
接聽電話並協助安排客人預約;
協助醫生完成簡單診症工作;
處理相關行政工作..

 要求:

中六畢業;
細心誠懇、具責任感，待人有禮及友善;
基本電腦操作;
能即時上班者優先.
